data.description: Charming 3 story house with dual staircases. One staircase in the kitchen and the other at the main entry way. Good size living and dining room with a half bathroom off the dining room on the main level. 3 bedrooms on the second floor and a full bathroom. the 3 floors could be used for additional bedrooms or bonus rooms.
